08:20.918 --> 08:22.085
(door opens)

08:22.285 --> 08:25.214
‐ LEIGH: Mr. Pearson.
‐ Yeah. Hello.

08:25.299 --> 08:26.717
Hi.

08:28.745 --> 08:30.830
‐ (sighs) ‐ It's a pleasure to meet you,
Randall.

08:30.915 --> 08:31.943
Please sit.

08:32.027 --> 08:34.445
Can I get you something
to drink?

08:34.553 --> 08:36.513
Um... likewise.

08:36.597 --> 08:38.515
And no, thank you.

08:38.599 --> 08:39.765
Uh...

08:39.850 --> 08:42.519
what's with the...?

08:42.602 --> 08:44.479
I find it comforting.

08:44.563 --> 08:47.524
Well, at least you'll
have something to look at

08:47.608 --> 08:48.859
if I bore you.

08:48.943 --> 08:50.611
(clears throat)

08:55.573 --> 08:58.534
So, what brings you here today?

08:58.619 --> 09:00.871
It's kind of a long story.

09:01.235 --> 09:03.278
You got an hour?

09:05.960 --> 09:07.544
(quietly):
Okay.

