What's it called?

30:06.633 --> 30:08.695
‐ The, the blowfish.
‐ Blowfish.

30:08.780 --> 30:10.698
‐ (chuckles): Yeah.
‐ Yes. (claps)

30:10.782 --> 30:12.628
Uh, yeah, I just... I don't want

30:12.713 --> 30:14.339
to reinforce
this family's narrative

30:14.424 --> 30:15.549
that I'm not dependable.

30:16.370 --> 30:18.164
