30:18.248 --> 30:19.707
They can wait until tomorrow.

30:19.791 --> 30:22.089
‐ Mom...
‐ (exhales)

30:22.395 --> 30:25.065
I don't... I don't want to go.

30:26.155 --> 30:28.324
'Cause I don't want
today to end.

30:31.994 --> 30:33.917
Today's gonna end
no matter what.

30:38.391 --> 30:40.230
But there's tomorrow.

30:40.570 --> 30:42.284
There's tomorrow,
and I will be here,

30:42.369 --> 30:44.413
and we will do something else.

30:45.495 --> 30:47.073
I promise.

30:50.978 --> 30:54.064
