this is a waste of time.

31:51.383 --> 31:52.800
I know my faults.

31:52.940 --> 31:54.284
I know what triggers me.

31:54.369 --> 31:56.745
But I think my faults
are good faults,

31:56.830 --> 31:59.082
and I would rather have them
than to not have them.

31:59.362 --> 32:01.446
And I know you think
I'm spiraling right now.

32:01.585 --> 32:03.337
I've seen the shows.
I know the drill.

32:03.422 --> 32:05.506
But, hey, if it wasn't for me,

32:05.591 --> 32:08.720
