are doing their homework.

33:24.037 --> 33:25.955
Right on.

33:26.234 --> 33:29.028
(grunts)

33:34.349 --> 33:36.009
(sighs)

33:40.902 --> 33:42.626
I tried, babe.

33:46.432 --> 33:48.350
I just don't think it's for me.

33:49.305 --> 33:51.071
I...

33:51.156 --> 33:52.360
Well, not...

33:52.445 --> 33:53.658
At least not right now.

33:53.742 --> 33:55.660
