this morning?

34:38.608 --> 34:39.900
Why?

34:55.018 --> 34:57.603
You bought Annie the iPhone.

34:57.992 --> 34:59.743
It's a bottle of pepper spray

35:00.643 --> 35:04.126
'cause sometimes I have to lock
up the studio alone at night.

35:04.264 --> 35:05.806
And that didn't used
to bother me,

35:05.891 --> 35:07.407
but now it does.

35:11.902 --> 35:13.977
This is doctor‐ prescribed.

35:15.249 --> 35:17.423
You know, I haven't been
sleeping very well.

35:18.499 --> 35:21.149
She gave me three pills
just to get me over the hump.

35:22.597 --> 35:23.743
And yeah.

35:23.885 --> 35:25.102
This is a phone for Annie,

35:25.187 --> 35:26.730
but it's not
because she wants it.

35:27.084 --> 35:29.002
It's because I want her
to have it

35:29.117 --> 35:32.411
because there was a strange man
in our house,

35:32.496 --> 35:35.415
and I need to know
where my baby is at all times.

35:35.500 --> 35:37.084
I'm sorry, Beth, I didn't know.

35:37.416 --> 35:39.334
Of course you didn't.

35:39.442 --> 35:41.360
'Cause I didn't tell you.

35:41.970 --> 35:43.430
Because I was worried

35:43.515 --> 35:45.976
that if I lay anything else
on you,

35:46.244 --> 35:48.071
